---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"tools\", \"update\", \"--help\"])"
---
Refresh tools to release defaults or config pins

For each managed tool, resolves the wanted version (config pin, else this release's default) and installs it if it is not already cached. A failure on one tool is reported and the run continues.

Usage: hpds tools update [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -v, --verbose
          Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)

  -q, --quiet
          Suppress all output except errors

      --no-color
          Disable colored output

      --config <PATH>
          Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
